lead_paragraph: Spanish authorities have detained 34 people, including six tennis players, involved in a tennis match-fixing network that made more than half-a-million dollars from lower-tier tournaments in Spain and Portugal.

headline.print_headline: 34 Spaniards Detained in Tennis Match-Fixing Investigation
